title: Microsoft Entra: SAML Certificates
agents: entra
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the expiration time of certificates
 from Entra enterprise applications with SAML SSO configured.

 The levels {OK}, {WARN} and {CRIT} depends on the
 configured check levels for the certificate expiration time.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft Entra}.

item:
 The name of the entra enterprise application.

discovery:
 One service is created for each entra enterprise application
 with SAML SSO configured.
